# Laravel — Test Patterns

## Stack context
- PHP 8.x, Laravel 9/10/11
- PHPUnit (built-in) + Pest (optional)
- Test runner: `php artisan test` hoặc `./vendor/bin/phpunit`

## Phân loại test

| Cần test gì | Class extends | Trait |
|---|---|---|
| HTTP endpoint, full stack | `TestCase` (Feature) | `RefreshDatabase` |
| Pure logic, không DB | `TestCase` (Unit) | Không cần |
| Console command | `TestCase` (Feature) | `RefreshDatabase` |
| Queue job | `TestCase` (Feature) | `RefreshDatabase` |

## Feature test (HTTP)
```php
class LoginTest extends TestCase
{
    use RefreshDatabase;

    public function test_returns_token_when_credentials_valid(): void
    {
        $user = User::factory()->create(['password' => bcrypt('secret')]);

        $response = $this->postJson('/api/login', [
            'email' => $user->email,
            'password' => 'secret',
        ]);

        $response->assertOk()->assertJsonStructure(['token']);
    }
}
```

## Unit test (service/action)
```php
class OrderCalculatorTest extends TestCase
{
    public function test_applies_discount_when_coupon_valid(): void
    {
        $calculator = new OrderCalculator();
        $total = $calculator->calculate(items: [...], coupon: 'SAVE10');
        $this->assertEquals(90.0, $total);
    }
}
```

## Factory pattern
```php
User::factory()->count(3)->create();
Product::factory()->state(['status' => 'active'])->create();
```

## Mock service
```php
$this->mock(PaymentGateway::class, function (MockInterface $mock) {
    $mock->shouldReceive('charge')->once()->andReturn(['status' => 'success']);
});
```

## Queue / Event fake
```php
Queue::fake();
Event::fake([OrderShipped::class]);
// ... trigger action
Queue::assertPushed(SendInvoiceJob::class);
```

## Test naming convention
`test_{expected_behavior}_when_{condition}`
hoặc (Pest): `it('returns token when credentials valid')`

## Database
- `RefreshDatabase` → migrate + rollback sau mỗi test (chậm hơn)
- `DatabaseTransactions` → rollback transaction (nhanh hơn, không chạy được với nhiều connection)
